                       4    ;*                    MCS-BASIC-52 V1.31 Source Listing                      *
                       5    ;*                           12/1986 till 11/2001                            *
                       6    ;*       The original source code of V1.1 (BASIC.SRC and FP52.SRC) by        *
                       7    ;*            Intel Corporation, Embedded Controller Operations              *
                       8    ;*                             is public donain                              *
