                     181    ; *MCS-51(tm) BASIC V1.1* to
                     182    ; *MCS-BASIC-52 V1.31*
                     183    ;
                     184    ; H.-J. Boehling, D. Wulf 11/26/2001
                     185    ;*****************************************************************************
